Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:18.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Minami...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:20.23,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.23,0:00:23.06,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Uhm... I'm sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:27.15,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Who cares? Why don't\Nyou go get cozy with Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:29.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't say things like that.\NPlease stop being upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:31.45,Main,,0,0,0,,And let's think up another strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.45,0:00:33.91,Main,,0,0,0,,If we end up fighting a\Nwar with Class B and lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:35.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji might have to change scho--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:37.41,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you saying, you dummy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:40.50,Main,,0,0,0,,With you, it's always\NMizuki this, Mizuki that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:42.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is Mizuki the only\Ngirl you treat like a princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:43.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Minami...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.63,0:00:46.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, what am I? Why do\Nyou always treat me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm a guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:50.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I-It's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:54.01,Main,,0,0,0,,If Mizuki's parents try to make her\Nchange schools, I'll go talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:00:55.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Minami...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:58.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't ever talk to me again!\NI don't wanna see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:08.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hi!! Question: Alone or together,{\i0}\N{\i1}which one is wonderful?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:27.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My future starts spinning colorfully{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.46,0:01:32.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How much should I tell him?{\i0}\N{\i1}Should I pretend I didn't see?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:38.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see, this vast world{\i0}\N{\i1}grows based on my mood{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:44.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you today, I really love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:49.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so stupid... My stupidity is greater{\i0}\N{\i1}than the number of the stars in the sky{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.28,0:01:55.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't admit my feelings for you,{\i0}\N{\i1}but I had a dream of walking with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:02:00.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry... It's just,{\i0}\N{\i1}I didn't know it was love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.29,0:02:07.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The answer is, you and mystery{\i0}\N{\i1}plus me equals infinite jump!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:29.06,Main,,0,0,0,,"BAKA and TEST\N-Summon the Beasts 2-"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:33.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Last episode recap. Woohoo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:37.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Class B rep, Kyouji Nemoto,{\i0}\N{\i1}was planning to declare war on Class F{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:43.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}since they just finished their suspension{\i0}\N{\i1}and so their fighting power is low.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:45.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, Akihisa and his friends in Class F{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:49.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}were trying to provoke Class D in order{\i0}\N{\i1}to get them to declare war on Class F.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:55.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If they fight Class D first, they'll{\i0}\N{\i1}be given time to take recovery tests.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:56.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If they rebuild their forces then,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:03:00.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Class B probably won't{\i0}\N{\i1}come and attack them so easily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:04.64,Main,,0,0,0,,In order to do that, we were going\Nto have Akihisa and Shimada pretend
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,to be dating and instigate\NMiharu Shimizu's anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:09.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that was our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:13.57,Main,,0,0,0,,That was a total failure, you dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:17.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Who'd think that you and\NShimada are dating after that scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:19.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:22.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I should've\Ngiven you more acting lessons...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:25.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Shimada and Himeji did a good job, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:28.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... Well... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:33.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do you treat me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:37.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Muttsulini, how are things in Class B?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:40.18,Main,,0,0,0,,They've currently recovered about 70%.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:42.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Some of them have already\Nstarted getting ready for the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:44.56,Main,,0,0,0,,They're moving faster than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:47.35,Main,,0,0,0,,That shows how serious they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:49.40,Main,,0,0,0,,We need to buy some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:53.11,Main,,0,0,0,,First, Muttsulini... Feed some\Nfake information to Class B.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:54.03,Main,,0,0,0,,What info?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:58.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Class D is preparing for an\NST War. Their target is Class B.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:00.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:02.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Would something like that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:07.37,Main,,0,0,0,,All Nemoto wants is to\Nwin and retain his position.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:10.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet he wants to avoid fighting a\Nseries of wars, which can exhaust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:12.79,Main,,0,0,0,,If he learns that Class D is after them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,he'll probably hesitate to declare war on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:20.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. Yeah, it's not like\Nthey want Class F's equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Next, Hideyoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:26.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Bring Miharu Shimizu from\NClass D to the negotiation table.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:29.81,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll provoke her and\Ninstigate her hostility towards us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:32.90,Main,,0,0,0,,If we can get them to\Ndeclare war on us, it's a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:34.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:38.11,Main,,0,0,0,,In order to bring her out,\Nwe need to bring Shimada.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Right now, we can't ask\NAkihisa or Himeji to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:43.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Also, Akihisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:49.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, I'm kinda hungry, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:53.38,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not good. You are the\Ncornerstone of this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:57.76,Main,,0,0,0,,We need to have you eat good to\Nboost up your energy... right, Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:05:02.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Yeah, you're right.\NIf he's hungry, he won't have energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:07.10,Main,,0,0,0,,So, Himeji... Could you make something to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:09.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Actually...! Now that I think about it,\NI already had lunch earlier, so I'm full.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:11.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't eat anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:13.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Lunch? You mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:14.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:15.86,Main,,0,0,0,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:18.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahhhhhh! How could you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:22.40,Main,,0,0,0,,So, Himeji, could you make\Nsomething to eat for Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:24.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure! I'd be happy to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji, uncle! Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:27.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa, what do you wanna eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:29.75,Main,,0,0,0,,What do I wanna eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:32.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I make a good choice, it will{\i0}\N{\i1}reduce the chances of fatality.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:35.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:36.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dish whose ingredients can be identified,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:39.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that won't have{\i0}\N{\i1}unexpected objects mixed in...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.92,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right! Boiled eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:42.26,Main,,0,0,0,,"Mizuki's Homemade Dish"\N"Today's Dish: Boiled Eggs" "Ingredients: Eggs only"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:45.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like... Akihisa wants to eat jello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:48.81,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't really tell what's in it, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:50.81,Main,,0,0,0,,In order for him to be able\Nto eat during the operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:52.94,Main,,0,0,0,,put it in jello drink aluminum pouches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:55.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't even check the color like that, can I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:57.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:06:00.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! At least decide what kind of\Njello you're gonna make before you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:04.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Akihisa.\NThat's not actually for you to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:05.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:08.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I just needed some weapons\Nfor our operation, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:11.79,Main,,0,0,0,,O-Oh... You should've told me sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:14.92,Main,,0,0,0,,But because of what I said, I think\Nshe's probably gonna try to have you eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You're too brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:17.84,Main,,0,0,0,,"Cooking Practice Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:23.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Getting gelatin and sugar ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:25.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, it seems unexpectedly normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:26.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:31.22,Main,,0,0,0,,First, dissolve the cocoa\Npowder in corn potage soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:33.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's she making?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:35.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Be quiet! She'll notice us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:40.15,Main,,0,0,0,,An orange or a scallion...\NI wonder which one Akihisa would like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:43.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't debate! You shouldn't\Ndebate between those two, Himeji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:47.82,Main,,0,0,0,,She's picking ingredients for you\Nbased on nutrition rather than taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:50.41,Main,,0,0,0,,If I have a scallion,\Nhow about adding {\i1}natto{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.29,Main,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:53.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\NI've heard that what they said
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:56.83,Main,,0,0,0,,about {\i1}natto {\i0}improving our\Nblood flow was a lie, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:57.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:00.05,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's still healthy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:06.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's blue-skinned fish\Nthat will improve the blood flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:07.47,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a double play...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:10.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Why vinegared mackerel? Why is\Nshe putting vinegared mackerel in jello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:15.64,Main,,0,0,0,,She's worried about you being stupid,\Nso she's trying to replenish your DHA.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:19.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! This isn't gonna be good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:21.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Good! Himeji noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to add mustard for the {\i1}natto{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:25.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't notice {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:26.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll add some ginger to\Nvinegared mackerel, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! Don't notice that, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:30.41,Main,,0,0,0,,What else can I use as secret ingredients?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:32.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't make it secret! Make it clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:35.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right! To give it a\Nlittle adultish flavor, I'll add taba--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go. If you hear any further,\Nyou won't be able to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:42.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Let me at least check\Nwhether it's tobacco or Tabasco!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's already too late.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, please have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:50.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go clean up the\Ncooking practice room, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.72,Main,,0,0,0,,What do we do with these?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:56.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I think Nemoto is gonna\Nsend a messenger to Class D...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:59.06,Main,,0,0,0,,...in order to check if they're\Nreally trying to fight a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:02.90,Main,,0,0,0,,If he does that, he'll know the\Ninformation we circulated was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.69,Main,,0,0,0,,So, we'll assassinate that messenger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:06.49,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:11.16,Main,,0,0,0,,If the messenger gets assassinated,\Nhe'll become distrustful of Class D.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:14.41,Main,,0,0,0,,When that happens, it'll make\Nthe fake information believable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.20,Main,,0,0,0,,How terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:19.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Battles are cruel. Muttsulini, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:21.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:25.55,Main,,0,0,0,,"Crack, crack"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:33.05,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:36.10,Main,,0,0,0,,"Buzz, buzz..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.23,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Messenger"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:40.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:42.27,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Messenger"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:43.77,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Messenger"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:45.27,Main,,0,0,0,,May God help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:57.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:00.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Execution completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:02.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Good job, Muttsulini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.92,Main,,0,0,0,,What fascinating skills you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.92,0:09:06.84,Main,,0,0,0,,This wasn't anything special...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:09.38,Main,,0,0,0,,How did you keep\Neveryone from noticing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.51,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:15.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Nemoto will probably consider this\Nassassination a warning from Class D.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:17.81,Main,,0,0,0,,We can buy some time now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:20.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Hideyoshi, what's going on\Nwith the negotiation with Class D?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:22.81,Main,,0,0,0,,We promised to meet\Nup in an empty classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:24.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Shimada has agreed to it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:27.44,Main,,0,0,0,,If we can provoke Class D there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:30.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they'll respond\Nto our provocation smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:33.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got a special plan.\NJust leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:36.08,Main,,0,0,0,,There's one thing that worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:38.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Muttsulini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:42.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I saw Nemoto talking\Nabout something in Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.88,Main,,0,0,0,,In Class A? That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:46.34,Main,,0,0,0,,What was he doing in Class A?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:48.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:50.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Shouko! Wh-What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:53.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are {\i1}you {\i0}still in school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:55.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:58.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji... I heard that your mom collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! You mean {\i1}my {\i0}mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.89,Main,,0,0,0,,She's so healthy that she\Ndoesn't even catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:06.19,Main,,0,0,0,,In any case, you have to go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:09.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! I have to carry out\Nan important operation now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:10.74,Main,,0,0,0,,This is no time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:13.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Like I said, just wait! How come you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:16.41,Main,,0,0,0,,--Just come with me.\N--Shouko! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:19.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Something is fishy\Nabout what just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:21.00,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Muttsulini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:24.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Normally, Yuuji is the\Nfirst one that they'd contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:29.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe they couldn't reach him?\NHis cell is being repaired, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:31.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Then they could've called\Nhim in via the school PA system.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:35.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, what Nemoto was\Ntalking about in Class A could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.43,Main,,0,0,0,,It was probably the fake\Ninformation that we just heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:38.22,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:43.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh shoot! We were going to leave the\Noperation to provoke Shimizu to Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:45.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Have you heard anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:45.94,Main,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.94,0:10:48.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did Nemoto do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:50.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he figured out our plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:53.82,Main,,0,0,0,,No, he's probably trying\Nto buy some time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:56.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Until he checks what\NClass D is going to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:58.91,Main,,0,0,0,,he probably wanted to\Ncontain our movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Impressive, Nemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.00,Main,,0,0,0,,It's about time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:05.83,Main,,0,0,0,,M-Minami...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:09.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I just came because I was needed\Nfor the negotiation, that's all, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:11.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What do we do, Akihisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:13.42,Main,,0,0,0,,What do we do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:15.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Since Yuuji isn't here, we have no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:17.93,Main,,0,0,0,,but to do something about it by ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:24.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idiot Test!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:35.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Honey! I wanted to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:38.24,Main,,0,0,0,,--Hey, get off of me, Miharu!\N--Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:42.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Your breasts remind me of\Nthe quiet ocean. They're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:45.75,Main,,0,0,0,,That means they're flat,\Njust like the horizon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:47.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I said, get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:51.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about you 360 days a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:54.00,Main,,0,0,0,,So you don't during {\i1}obon{\i0}\Nfestivities and New Year's, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:58.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Shimizu, that's it!\NShimada is Akihisa's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:00.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't intervene thoughtlessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:02.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There you go!{\i0}\N{\i1}The start of our operation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:04.93,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:07.31,Main,,0,0,0,,By looking at my\Nhoney's face, it's so obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:11.40,Main,,0,0,0,,that there's nothing going on\Nbetween her and that big jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:14.98,Main,,0,0,0,,It's hard to think that that pig jerk\Nis suitable for her in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:19.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I-It's true that I'm not good-looking\Nand I'm not smart, either, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:22.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks? Smarts?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:26.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about such trivial things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:28.00,Main,,0,0,0,,This is something\Nmore fundamental than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.79,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:33.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been watching the\Nrelationship between the two of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:36.13,Main,,0,0,0,,but your attitude is terrible, you pig jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:38.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Your attitude towards Himeji in the same class
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:42.43,Main,,0,0,0,,and towards my honey are too different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:47.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You're kind and considerate to Himeji.\NYou treat her as if she's a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:50.23,Main,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, you aren't\Nconsiderate to my honey. Not only that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:53.44,Main,,0,0,0,,you don't even show the least bit of\Nkindness you should have towards girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:59.70,Main,,0,0,0,,To put it plainly, you are a huge idiot\Nwho not only doesn't notice her charms
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:03.03,Main,,0,0,0,,but who treats her like a guy friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:06.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Whether such a pig jerk is\Nsuitable for her or not is not a question
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:08.62,Main,,0,0,0,,of his looks or his academic abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:12.96,Main,,0,0,0,,On top of that, to think that you'd\Nleave her alone and follow Himeji like that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:16.75,Main,,0,0,0,,after she told you she liked you,\Neven though she was acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.21,Main,,0,0,0,,That's unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:21.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't the truth that you\Nthink she's a guy or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:26.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Minami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.93,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you gonna do by following her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:33.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna talk to her rough\Nagain as if she's your guy friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:35.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna hurt her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go talk to her. If you go,\Nit'll make things worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:46.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Err... I don't know what's going on,\Nbut I should leave, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:55.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you wanted\Nto achieve with this meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.09,0:14:00.34,Main,,0,0,0,,but I'll never acknowledge\Nyou as my rival in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:06.26,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a waste of time to be jealous of a\Npig jerk who doesn't notice her charms, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:11.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who recognizes her charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:13.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Shimizu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:16.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you still have something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:20.11,Main,,0,0,0,,There's something I have\Nto tell you no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:39.29,Main,,0,0,0,,We, Year 2 Class D, are\Ngoing to declare war on Class F!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:41.26,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:42.59,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:44.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't our plan fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:51.47,Main,,0,0,0,,So what're we gonna do after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.77,Main,,0,0,0,,It'd be hard to win with\Nour current fighting power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.73,Main,,0,0,0,,That was in my plan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:56.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:59.27,Main,,0,0,0,,As I suspected, it was fake\Ninformation planted by Nemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:01.36,Main,,0,0,0,,My mom is doing better than fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:03.40,Main,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:05.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Good job, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:07.41,Main,,0,0,0,,It wasn't exactly how I planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:09.95,Main,,0,0,0,,but if you were able to\Ninstigate Shimizu, that's a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:13.62,Main,,0,0,0,,So, Yuuji, how are we gonna fight Class D?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:16.29,Main,,0,0,0,,If we fight in an all-out\Nbattle, we have no chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:19.96,Main,,0,0,0,,So we'll settle this with a\Nbattle between representatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:28.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed that you\Ncame without running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:30.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:33.60,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not that I want to fight my honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:37.39,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as I can beat the crap\Nout of that pig jerk, that'll do for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:42.27,Main,,0,0,0,,So she says. It's now\Nyour mission from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:43.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:45.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:48.82,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the one person\NI can never forgive! Be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:50.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Teacher! Please give\Nus summoning approval!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:51.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I approve!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:55.79,Main,,0,0,0,,--Summon!\N--Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:59.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanna ask you something first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:00.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:04.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Was what you said a\Ntrick to start this war?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:09.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I... see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:14.10,Main,,0,0,0,,My honey was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:17.31,Main,,0,0,0,,My words triggered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:22.77,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's because... it's\Nbecause a guy like you exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:24.44,Main,,0,0,0,,"Chemistry"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:28.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is a lout like you by her side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:34.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is a vulgar man who plays on\Nher feelings conversing with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:36.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:40.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Why does a bastard who lies to her\Nlike it's nothing in order to use her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:43.04,Main,,0,0,0,,stay close to her,\Npretending to be her friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:49.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not... lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:53.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Even an idiot like me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:57.06,Main,,0,0,0,,at least knows there are\Nsome lies you should never tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:16:59.35,Main,,0,0,0,,What I said wasn't a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it!\NI don't wanna believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:05.61,Main,,0,0,0,,What I said was\Nunmistakably my true feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:10.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:16.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:25.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.96,Main,,0,0,0,,From here, just leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:30.26,Main,,0,0,0,,How dirty! This is foul play!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:35.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Call it foul play if you like!\NThis isn't a game! It's a war!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:37.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:38.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji! Sto--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:50.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Ow, ow, ow...! Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:52.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow! Ow, ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:54.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...! Ow, ow, ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:57.74,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! What?! This\Ncombination of sharp and dull pain
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:18:00.37,Main,,0,0,0,,is breaking new ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.75,0:18:06.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Shimizu... As you can see, the main\Ncause of all the problems is cleaned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:10.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you forget what\Nhappened this time and forgive him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:15.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah... My fury still isn't cooled down,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:18.43,Main,,0,0,0,,but if this pig jerk will be\Nconfined to the remedial classroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:20.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll accept the cease-fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:23.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that you were\Nplanning this from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:28.78,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can win against\NClass D with our current forces, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:31.24,Main,,0,0,0,,So it's just natural to\Nnegotiate a cease-fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:35.03,Main,,0,0,0,,When we get right down to it,\Nyou're at fault for hurting my honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:39.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry! I'm sorry from the\Nbottom of my... Ow, ow, ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:44.08,Main,,0,0,0,,If what you said was a lie, I wouldn't\Nhave let you get off the hook this easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:50.42,Main,,0,0,0,,But this time, I'll let\Nyou off the hook with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:54.17,Main,,0,0,0,,The deal is done. Guys! Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:04.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:07.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thus, the war ended.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.73,Main,,0,0,0,,How was it, Muttsulini?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:12.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like Nemoto from Class B gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:14.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that was expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:17.95,Main,,0,0,0,,There's already no benefit to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:20.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Also, I went and collected this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:22.33,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:24.12,Main,,0,0,0,,--I don't know what you wanted to achieve with this meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.12,Main,,0,0,0,,--D-Don't tell me this is...\N--I don't know what you wanted to achieve with this meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:26.29,Main,,0,0,0,,--D-Don't tell me this is...\N--but I'll never acknowledge you as my rival in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:28.71,Main,,0,0,0,,--The wiretapped recording of the summit conference.\N--but I'll never acknowledge you as my rival in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:33.01,Main,,0,0,0,,H-H-H-H-Hey! What're you playing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:34.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold him down good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:35.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:38.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Let go of me, Hideyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:41.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:44.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You're too noisy. Shut up for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:46.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you still have something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:50.82,Main,,0,0,0,,There's something I have\Nto tell you no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:53.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanna clear up just\None misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:57.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I already know that you\Nand my honey dating is an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:20:00.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:02.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:06.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to say that you're not the\Nonly one who recognizes Minami's charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:08.12,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:10.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You're always saying mean things to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:13.80,Main,,0,0,0,,and you don't even cherish her as a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:17.80,Main,,0,0,0,,It's true that I don't\Ntreat her like a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:23.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I might be treating her\Njust like I treat my guy friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.64,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:28.02,Main,,0,0,0,,But... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:32.61,Main,,0,0,0,,To me, Minami is someone whom\NI can be my true self around...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:35.28,Main,,0,0,0,,...who is fun to hang out with...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:38.61,Main,,0,0,0,,...and who sometimes makes\Nsubtle gestures that are cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:43.37,Main,,0,0,0,,She's very charming...\NYeah, she's a charming girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:48.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... that was unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:53.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I thought you'd say\Nthings a little more indirectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:56.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That was a straight pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:59.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-They heard it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:01.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Of all people, these three heard it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:04.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize that you\Ncan say things boldly like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:09.44,Main,,0,0,0,,F-For some reason, my\Nheart is beating crazy fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.44,0:21:11.15,Main,,0,0,0,,How bold...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:14.90,Main,,0,0,0,,My life... is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:17.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Noin, stretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:20.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, Big Sis! Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:22.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:25.49,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Your face is red!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.49,0:21:27.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Haduki, what am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:31.67,Main,,0,0,0,,About what? Did\Nsomething happen at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:34.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Haduki...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:35.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:41.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I might've fallen hopelessly\Nin love with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:51.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flash! Shine! Light bulb, shiny flash!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:07.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not making progress.{\i0}\N{\i1}Someone's interfering... No, no!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:12.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The issue is, I don't have{\i0}\N{\i1}enough common multiples{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.92,0:22:17.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, I basically get it.{\i0}\N{\i1}What is the truth... Baby?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.67,0:22:23.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you see this, draw a{\i0}\N{\i1}diagram and explain it, Baby!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:29.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No word or number can describe you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.14,0:22:37.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My heart is being shocked by{\i0}\N{\i1}the magnetic force between S and N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.19,0:22:41.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(S! S! Super! Sticking together,{\i0}\N{\i1}Number! I say No.1 boy!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:47.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Congratulations! From here on{\i0}\N{\i1}out you're My, ma-my "treasure"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.33,0:22:50.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're special to me,{\i0}\N{\i1}no matter what happens{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:52.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll hold you ever so{\i0}\N{\i1}tight and never let you go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:58.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to be in love, in a{\i0}\N{\i1}dream you can forget about limits{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.13,0:23:01.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's special, right? After all,{\i0}\N{\i1}we came to know each other{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:04.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive me for being like this{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.13,0:23:09.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flashed! Shined! Right answer, perfect match!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.64,0:23:20.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm dreading this. What do I say to\Napologize to Minami when I see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:23.49,Main,,0,0,0,,--Hey.\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.32,0:23:27.91,Main,,0,0,0,,What's with that gloomy face, Aki?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:29.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.41,0:23:30.91,Main,,0,0,0,,M-Minami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:31.99,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.99,0:23:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, uhm... Er...\NI'm sorry about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.12,0:23:39.92,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Did you do something\Nagain that you have to apologize for?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.92,0:23:41.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.59,0:23:45.09,Main,,0,0,0,,If you cause another problem,\NI won't let you off the hook!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.09,0:23:46.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.72,0:23:50.85,Main,,0,0,0,,You dummy!
